
		ARRAY															COLLECTION

These are of fixed size 		 ||				It is growable as per requirement it can grow and shrink as well
It contains only homogeneous means similar type of elements || It has both homo and hetrogeneous types of elements
Array is a class 				|| 				It's an Interface
No readymade methods are available ||			Supports readymade methods like sorting, add, remove etc
Memory utilization is bad			||		Memory utilization is good here
Performance is faster				|| 		Performance wise Array are better 					